== Rama ==

Ram Vixnnuchea dha ovtarantlo satvo ovtar. Ikxvaku kullantlo iodhyecho raza Doxroth ani patt'ttoranni Kouslea hancho put. Obheasokanchea motan tacho kall i.so. adim 2000 te 1950. Tachi zolmotith choitr xu. nom' (ramonm') Valomiki munichea "Ramainn" hea mhakaveant to adorx put, ekoptnivorti, mhaprakromi, sorvoxrextth zhuzari ani adorx rajio oxem Ramachem vornnon kelam. Nardan tachevixim vornnon kelam tem oxem- ikxvaku kullantlo ram' ho adorx pururx, sobit mukhamoll, vixal kopol, vhodd dolle, purai kuddicher agllich kanti axil'lo, vidhiet khampo, rajnitigone, sojzonacho songroh ani durzonacho nigroh korpi, dhorm', orth ani kam' hea tinui puruxarthanchem iogio toren sevon korpi, songit, vade, chitrkola hatunt huxar, projahitokxod ani projnonank prio osom ho Ram xrextth purux. Raza Doxorthak Kouslea, Sumitra ani Koiko-i oxo tin Ranneo axil'leo. Tankam boroch temp bhurgim zali na. Tannem rixioxrring muni vorvim putrokamextthi yogn kelo. Tedna Kouslieger Ram, Sumitrager Lokxmonn ani Xotrud'n ani Koikeyiger Bhorot oxe char put zale. Soglle put gineannani, gunni ani huxar axil'le. Ram ho hoteacher ani ghoddeacher bospant ani rothsoncholon korpant fixal axil'lo. To pondra vorsancho astona aple iogonebhuimek rakxosamposun rakhonn mellchi dekhun vixrvomitr Rixi taka gheun gelo. Thoim tannem Ramak bola ani otibla heo zhuzvidea xikoileo. Tea vellar Raman, Tattoka he Rakxoxinnik jivexim marli. Toxench marich, subahu adi rakxosank dhanvddavn ghale. Tedana vixvamitran khoxi zavn Ramak divio ostram dilim. Uprant Vixrvamitran taka mithilek zonok razager vholo. Vattent Raman goutom Rixichi bail ohilea hika xapmukt keli.


mithilek raman xivdhonnu ubarun aplem bollgem dakhoile uprant zonkorazan tachem ani sitechim logn lavn dilem. jen'na doxorthak ramacho iuvrajeabhixek korpacho tharailo ten'na koikeyin ramak chovda vorsam vonvas ani bhortak iuvrajeabhixenk oxe don vor magun ghetle. bapaiche agoneek pallo divpak ram' vonvasak vochunk bhair sorlo. ten'na tachevangdda sita ani lokxmonnio vonvasak gelim. jen'na tim chitrkutt porvotacher pavlim ten'na bhorot tankam porot aiodhyek vhorpak ailo. tannem ramak doxroth morpachi khobor dili ani oiodhyek porot vochpak vinoilem.raman bapaik dil'lem vochon moddunk nhoinkar dilo ten'na bhortan tacheo paduka oiodhyek vhorun tanche prernnen tannem rajkarbhar choloilo. thoinchean ram', lokxmonn, sita otri rixichea axromant gelim. thoim sitechi ani toposvini onusuiechim bhett zali. thoinchean tim donddkarnneant gelim. thoim tamnni dha vorsa sarlim. zaite mhoine tamnni rixinchea vegvegllea axromant vosnnuk keli. heach kallant ogos'tio rixin ramak divio dhonnu dilem. ponchvottint astona ramak zaitea norobhokxok rakxosancho nax kelo. ravonnachi bhoinn xurponnokhecho tor lokxmonnan kan ani nak kapun opman kelo. te uprant ravonnan jen'na sitek ubarun vheli. ten'na ramak khub vaitt dislem. to lokxmonnavangdda ticho sod ghevk laglo. vatter tanka sugriv mell'lle.


ani honuman meloioioille. tacheam adaran tannem ravnnakodde zhuz korun sitechi suttka keli. tori tannem sitecho svikar korche adim tika ogniprikxa divchi poddli. ram' oiodhient porot ietokoch tacho rajiobhixek kelo. kaim disamni lokopvadak lagun tannem gurvar sitek valomiki axrmant soddli. thoim tinnem lavo ani kux hea don zuvllea bhurgeank zolm' dilo. thoim valomikin tankam apnnem rochil'lem mohakavio gaupak xikoilem. hea donoi kumaramni ramak tem gavn dakhoilem. uprant raman oxroumedh yogn kelo, ramachea adorx jinnecho ani ramainnacho bharoti-i ani brihodbharoti-i kolasahiteacher khol chhap utthil'lo dista. boud'dh ani join sahiteacher ramkothecho probhav poddla. boud'dh dhormat ram' ho bodhisot'tov, zalear join dhormat to atthvo bol'dev manun sahitiponirmiti zal'li asa. somskrit, prakrit ani prodexik bhasant ramkothaprosongacher zaitim mohakaveam, nattkam, chompukaveam ani khonddkaveam boroileant. ramlila, sarkea loknatteacher toxench lokgitantoi ramchoritracho probhav poddil'lo disun ieta. bharotabhair tibett, khotan, zanva, molea, soiam', brohradex, komboddia (khmer) adi dexantoi ramkothecho ovixkar zal'lo asa. hachebhair nach, nattok, chitram, xilpam, adi kolamvorvim-i ramjinnentlea prosongacho sobit avixkar disun ieta

rajput ani kangra xoilint ramoinnachea prosongachi zaiti chitram asat. zodhpur songrohaloiantolea farsi ramoinnachem protint 76 sobit chitram mellttat. namnecho chitrkar rovivorma hannem-i ramainnantlea kaim prosongancher sobit chitram mellttat. namnecho chitrkar rovivorma hannem-i ramainnantlea kaim prosongancher sobit chitronn kel'lem asa. verullchea koilas lenneant, hollebitth, hompi, kumbhkonnm', chondrgiri, devgoddh, oiholle, pohaddpur (bongal), nagarzunokondda toxench rajsthanantlea kenkida, kivaddu (ji. barmer), kheddo (ronnchhoddoram'), devull adi devllantlean ramkothentlea venchik prosongancho kolatmok avixkar disun ieta.

